➜【夏日茶食】普洱玫瑰消暑粥
http://www.sohu.com/a/411519226_100049042	6976
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200805/f6db3f61d8664d36a6bc9c4242ba6f8d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">主料：稻米150克</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200805/8cf1a6e836db4c12a4ca1ec815145cef.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">辅料：茶叶10克（生熟皆可），玫瑰花10克</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200805/88dd79d0feb449ffa682f643219ce05c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
